      <npc_text>“Don’t be so modest, *&lt;brother/sister&gt;*. It wasn’t a message, it was an ultimatum. Now Meru is dead and you want to rule his domain because the Gods told you to.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“The Gods made their wishes abundantly clear.”</text>
