          </linksOnClick>
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[streetwise]“Let's say you're right. Changes are coming. You can try to stop them and be swept away or be their agent. Hardly a difficult choice for a man who's been known to switch sides for less.”</text>
